I have two minor issues with this; you use the word  in its definition for the word). I'd consider replacing it with something else. The other issue is that I'm not into the separated blocks for each specific anomalous effect in your description. I can see why you did it, from a separation of information + text flow point of view, but it just doesn't work for me.

Neither of those points are too big though, so +1 from me.







